sequenceDiagram
    actor U as User
    participant FE as React SPA
    participant BE as NestJS API
    participant BA as Better-Auth
    participant MAIL as Nodemailer
    participant DB as MariaDB

    U->>FE: Submit registration form
    FE->>BE: POST /auth/sign-up
    BE->>BA: createUser(email, hash(password))
    BA->>DB: INSERT User (emailVerified=false)
    BA->>MAIL: sendVerificationEmail(token)
    MAIL-->>U: Verification email
    BA-->>BE: 201 Created
    BE-->>FE: 201 + session cookie (pending verification)
    FE-->>U: "Check your inbox" screen

    Note over U,DB: Email verification
    U->>FE: Click verification link
    FE->>BE: GET /auth/verify-email?token=...
    BE->>BA: verifyToken(token)
    BA->>DB: UPDATE User SET emailVerified=true
    BA-->>BE: OK
    BE-->>FE: Redirect /email-verified
    FE-->>U: "Account verified" page

    Note over U,DB: Login
    U->>FE: Submit login form
    FE->>BE: POST /auth/sign-in
    BE->>BA: authenticate(email, password)
    BA->>DB: SELECT User
    BA-->>BE: Session token (JWT)
    BE-->>FE: 200 + Set-Cookie session
    FE-->>U: Redirect to dashboard
